u880
====

A cycle-stepped, dependency-free MME U880 emulator, port of Andre Weissflog's
z80.h with the U880-specific block I/O carry behavior patched in. Passes both
the ZEXDOC and ZEXALL tests.

    https://github.com/floooh/chips

